<%= render "marketing_nav" %>

<%# Hero %>
<section class="relative flex min-h-[90vh] items-center overflow-hidden landing-border border-b pt-20">
  <div class="landing-grid-bg pointer-events-none absolute inset-0"></div>
  <div class="relative mx-auto max-w-7xl px-6">
    <div class="max-w-4xl">
      <p class="landing-label mb-4">For Philippine Cooperatives</p>
      <h1 class="landing-hero-title text-5xl font-light leading-none tracking-[-0.04em] landing-text sm:text-6xl lg:text-7xl">
        Cooperative banking<br>
        <span class="landing-accent">without the busywork.</span>
      </h1>
      <p class="mt-6 max-w-2xl text-lg leading-relaxed landing-muted">
        Sirib handles the repetition so your tellers, loan officers, and finance team can focus 
        on the people they serve. One system for member accounts, loans, savings, cash sessions, 
        and financial reporting — with zero data re-entry.
      </p>
      <div class="mt-10 flex items-center gap-4">
        <a href="#features" class="landing-btn-accent px-8 py-3 text-sm font-semibold tracking-wide uppercase transition-colors">See What It Does</a>
        <a href="<%= new_session_path %>" class="landing-border-muted border px-8 py-3 text-sm font-medium tracking-wide landing-muted uppercase transition-colors hover:landing-btn-outline">Sign In</a>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="mt-20 grid grid-cols-1 gap-px landing-border border-t pt-8 sm:grid-cols-3">
      <div class="py-4">
        <p class="font-mono text-2xl font-light landing-text">8,000+</p>
        <p class="mt-1 text-sm landing-hero-stat-label">members served daily on Sirib</p>
      </div>
      <div class="py-4">
        <p class="font-mono text-2xl font-light landing-text">48 hrs</p>
        <p class="mt-1 text-sm landing-hero-stat-label">from sign-up to first transaction</p>
      </div>
      <div class="py-4">
        <p class="font-mono text-2xl font-light landing-text">100%</p>
        <p class="mt-1 text-sm landing-hero-stat-label">of coops that started stayed</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<%# Automate the work nobody wants to do %>
<section class="landing-border border-b" id="features">
  <div class="mx-auto max-w-7xl px-6 py-32">
    <div class="mx-auto max-w-3xl">
      <p class="landing-label mb-4">Everything You Need, Nothing You Don't</p>
      <h2 class="text-3xl font-light tracking-[-0.03em] landing-text sm:text-4xl">
        Automate the work <span class="landing-accent">nobody wants to do.</span>
      </h2>
    </div>
    <div class="mt-16 grid gap-px sm:grid-cols-2">
      <div class="landing-card border p-10">
        <p class="text-base font-medium landing-text">Transactions post automatically.</p>
        <p class="mt-2 text-sm leading-relaxed landing-muted">Deposits, withdrawals, loan payments — process once, and every related account updates. Cash position, member balance, journal entries, and daily totals all reflect the same transaction. No duplicate entry, no reconciliation chase.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="landing-card border p-10">
        <p class="text-base font-medium landing-text">Cash sessions that close in one click.</p>
        <p class="mt-2 text-sm leading-relaxed landing-muted">Tellers start their shift, process transactions, and end the day with a button. The system counts, compares, and flags discrepancies. What used to take 45 minutes of manual counting takes seconds.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="landing-card border p-10">
        <p class="text-base font-medium landing-text">Member profiles that tell the full story.</p>
        <p class="mt-2 text-sm leading-relaxed landing-muted">Savings accounts, loan history, share capital, transaction log — all on one screen. Loan officers see the complete picture before the member finishes explaining their situation.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="landing-card border p-10">
        <p class="text-base font-medium landing-text">Reports that write themselves.</p>
        <p class="mt-2 text-sm leading-relaxed landing-muted">Trial balance is always current. Financial statements, BSP compliance reports, and dashboards draw from the same data. Month-end is a day of review, not two weeks of matching spreadsheets.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<%# One source of truth %>
<section class="landing-border border-b landing-bg-alt">
  <div class="mx-auto max-w-7xl px-6 py-32">
    <div class="mx-auto max-w-3xl">
      <p class="landing-label mb-4">One Source of Truth</p>
      <h2 class="text-3xl font-light tracking-[-0.03em] landing-text sm:text-4xl">
        Every department posts to <span class="landing-accent">the same system.</span>
      </h2>
      <p class="mt-6 text-lg leading-relaxed landing-muted">
        No more teller logbooks that don't match the loan officer's spreadsheet that doesn't 
        match finance's reconciliation. When one person enters data, everyone works with the 
        same numbers — in real time.
      </p>
    </div>
    <div class="mt-12 grid gap-px sm:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-4">
      <div class="landing-card border p-8">
        <p class="text-sm font-medium landing-text">For tellers</p>
        <p class="mt-2 text-sm leading-relaxed landing-muted">Process once. Cash, passbook, and journal update together. End-of-day is a button.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="landing-card border p-8">
        <p class="text-sm font-medium landing-text">For loan officers</p>
        <p class="mt-2 text-sm leading-relaxed landing-muted">Full member profile. Automated amortisation. Payment posts everywhere at once.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="landing-card border p-8">
        <p class="text-sm font-medium landing-text">For finance</p>
        <p class="mt-2 text-sm leading-relaxed landing-muted">Trial balance on demand. BSP reports from the same data. Close in days, not weeks.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="landing-card border p-8">
        <p class="text-sm font-medium landing-text">For compliance</p>
        <p class="mt-2 text-sm leading-relaxed landing-muted">Audit trails that track every change. Cash positions you can trust without recounting.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<%# App Screenshots %>
<section class="landing-border border-b">
  <div class="mx-auto max-w-7xl px-6 py-32">
    <p class="landing-label mb-4">What It Looks Like</p>
    <h2 class="text-3xl font-light tracking-[-0.03em] landing-text sm:text-4xl">
      The same workflows,<br class="hidden sm:block">
      <span class="landing-accent">without the repetitive work.</span>
    </h2>
