<%# How the transition works %>
<section class="landing-border border-b landing-bg-alt" id="how">
  <div class="mx-auto max-w-7xl px-6 py-32">
    <div class="mx-auto max-w-3xl text-center">
      <p class="landing-label mb-4">How the Transition Works</p>
      <h2 class="text-3xl font-light tracking-[-0.03em] landing-text sm:text-4xl">
        Up and running in days, not months.<br>
        <span class="landing-accent">Your old system stays open until you're ready.</span>
      </h2>
    </div>
    <div class="mt-16 space-y-4">
      <div class="landing-card border p-8 flex items-start gap-6">
        <span class="font-mono text-2xl font-light landing-accent shrink-0 leading-none">1</span>
        <div>
          <p class="text-lg font-medium landing-text">We watch how your coop works today</p>
          <p class="mt-1 text-sm leading-relaxed landing-muted">We spend time with your tellers, loan officers, and finance team to understand their daily rhythm. No judgement, no assumptions — just learning what they do and what slows them down.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="landing-card border p-8 flex items-start gap-6">
        <span class="font-mono text-2xl font-light landing-accent shrink-0 leading-none">2</span>
        <div>
          <p class="text-lg font-medium landing-text">Your staff uses both side by side</p>
          <p class="mt-1 text-sm leading-relaxed landing-muted">Member records and account data are loaded into Sirib. Your team processes transactions in the new tool while keeping their familiar system as backup. There's no pressure to switch — just curiosity.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="landing-card border p-8 flex items-start gap-6">
        <span class="font-mono text-2xl font-light landing-accent shrink-0 leading-none">3</span>
        <div>
          <p class="text-lg font-medium landing-text">Your team decides when to make it official</p>
          <p class="mt-1 text-sm leading-relaxed landing-muted">Every day during parallel use, numbers are compared. When your finance team is confident everything matches, you pick the day. Some coops switch after a week. Some take two.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="landing-card border p-8 flex items-start gap-6">
        <span class="font-mono text-2xl font-light landing-accent shrink-0 leading-none">4</span>
        <div>
          <p class="text-lg font-medium landing-text">Help is there when you need it</p>
          <p class="mt-1 text-sm leading-relaxed landing-muted">On-site or video support during your first week fully on Sirib. After that, chat support during all operating hours. Most coops find their team is self-sufficient by day three.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<%# Testimonials %>
<section id="stories" class="landing-border border-b">
  <div class="mx-auto max-w-7xl px-6 py-32">
    <p class="landing-label mb-4">From Coops That Made the Move</p>
    <h2 class="text-3xl font-light tracking-[-0.03em] landing-text sm:text-4xl">
      What cooperative leaders<span class="landing-accent"> are saying</span>
    </h2>
    <div class="mt-16 grid gap-px sm:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-3">
      <div class="landing-card border p-8">
        <p class="text-sm leading-relaxed landing-muted">"Our tellers had been handwriting passbooks for decades. They were the most skeptical when we started. By day two, they were showing me how end-of-day used to take 45 minutes of counting — now it's done before the last member leaves."</p>
        <div class="mt-6 landing-border border-t pt-4">
          <p class="text-sm font-medium landing-text">General Manager</p>
          <p class="text-xs landing-dim">Luzon Cooperative</p>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="landing-card border p-8">
        <p class="text-sm leading-relaxed landing-muted">"Our loan officer kept everything in ring binders — not because she was disorganised, but because the systems she had didn't talk to each other. When she saw a member's complete profile appear on one screen, she said it felt like getting an assistant."</p>
        <div class="mt-6 landing-border border-t pt-4">
          <p class="text-sm font-medium landing-text">Operations Manager</p>
          <p class="text-xs landing-dim">Visayas Cooperative</p>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="landing-card border p-8">
        <p class="text-sm leading-relaxed landing-muted">"I spent three years trying to get board approval. Every vendor wanted a long commitment and a price tag that scared everyone. Sirib was running alongside our old setup in a weekend. The board saw the difference — and our team never felt forced."</p>
        <div class="mt-6 landing-border border-t pt-4">
          <p class="text-sm font-medium landing-text">Treasurer</p>
          <p class="text-xs landing-dim">Mindanao Cooperative</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<%# FAQs %>
<section class="landing-border border-b landing-bg-alt">
  <div class="mx-auto max-w-3xl px-6 py-32">
    <p class="landing-label mb-4">Questions You Might Have</p>
    <h2 class="text-3xl font-light tracking-[-0.03em] landing-text sm:text-4xl">
      FAQs
    </h2>
    <div class="mt-12 space-y-6">
      <div class="landing-card border p-8">
        <p class="text-base font-medium landing-text">Will my staff have time to learn this?</p>
        <p class="mt-2 text-sm leading-relaxed landing-muted">Most coops find their team is faster on Sirib within two days. It mirrors the way they already work — just without the repetition. During parallel use, there's zero pressure; staff can switch back anytime.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="landing-card border p-8">
        <p class="text-base font-medium landing-text">What if my older staff struggles with the technology?</p>
        <p class="mt-2 text-sm leading-relaxed landing-muted">Sirib is used daily by tellers who've spent 20 years handwriting passbooks. The interface is built for people who aren't tech enthusiasts — clear labels, few clicks, no jargon. On-site support is available during your first week.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="landing-card border p-8">
        <p class="text-base font-medium landing-text">How long does implementation take?</p>
        <p class="mt-2 text-sm leading-relaxed landing-muted">Member records and chart of accounts can be loaded over a weekend. Most coops are running side by side with their old system within 48 hours of deciding to start.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="landing-card border p-8">
        <p class="text-base font-medium landing-text">What if we lose data or have downtime?</p>
        <p class="mt-2 text-sm leading-relaxed landing-muted">Your old tools stay available during the transition. We only move fully when your team confirms they're comfortable. No forced cutover dates. And Sirib runs on secure cloud infrastructure with automatic backups.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="landing-card border p-8">
        <p class="text-base font-medium landing-text">Is Sirib compliant with BSP regulations?</p>
        <p class="mt-2 text-sm leading-relaxed landing-muted">Yes. Sirib generates reports aligned with BSP reporting requirements, maintains full audit trails on every transaction, and supports the chart of accounts structure cooperatives need for regulatory filings.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="landing-card border p-8">
        <p class="text-base font-medium landing-text">Can we keep our existing account numbering?</p>
        <p class="mt-2 text-sm leading-relaxed landing-muted">Absolutely. Sirib imports your existing member IDs, account numbers, and loan reference numbers. Members see no change — their account is the same, their passbook prints the same way.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<%# CTA %>
<section id="demo" class="landing-border border-b">
  <div class="mx-auto max-w-3xl px-6 py-32 text-center">
    <p class="landing-label mb-4">No Pitch. Just Proof.</p>
    <h2 class="text-3xl font-light tracking-[-0.03em] landing-text sm:text-4xl">
      See the tools your team would use every day.<br>
